data.description: Spacious 2 Story 4-bedroom home, available in Lancaster, Texas. No HOA. New carpet being replaced upstairs and on the stairwell leading upstairs. The fireplace compliments the family living area. Great home for first time buyers. Nice neighborhood and quick access to near downtown Dallas. The Master bedroom is downstairs. Nice size front yard and 2,700 plus feet of living space. All offers are welcomed.
